      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RAVEN FLY (6) did a good job to finish second last time out over 400m at this track (23.51) in a Maiden, the second top-three finish on the trot. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Can make amends this time. HOT TO TRACE (1) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (23.10) at Maitland behind More Drama in a Maiden. Stalked the pace but found the line strongly. Leading chance. MONSTRANCE CLOCK (4) stalked the lead and fought on well to finish 4 lengths away in third (22.92) at Gosford in a Maiden over 388m. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. ZIPPING SHYANN (2) is a Leeanne Goodwin-trained newcomer by Zipping Kyrgios out of Shoshe. Drawn favourably and can capitalise. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability.",
